{"tid":1025482,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"港女唔好再以為自己在愛情中唔洗付出","createTime":"2019-02-17T11:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T14:19:59.000Z","uid":224885,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"16cf15e5db325c809f38a69f384dfdb2fffa2c0b","tid":1025482,"uid":224885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:20:39.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n真係咪以為要人係你身邊出錢係正常 應該<br />\n為你做任何事係理所當然既觀念<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為你出錢 出力係因為真心愛你<br />\n你拎住人地對你既愛黎當作藉口 咩都唔做 咩都要<br />\n唔出錢就話唔愛你 <br />\n唔做少少野就黑哂面 唔講以為去左非洲住<br />\n<br />\n你付出過咩？ <br />\n收收埋埋咁多野 咁多兵唔比人知<br />\n一句私人黎<br />\n搵到第二件水魚就走？<br />\n你講哂 玩撚哂啦<br />\n<br />\n好好珍惜真心愛你 為你付出既人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce6606bb13edd4db58f15aa5ec77f4fddb1e3df","tid":1025482,"uid":27064,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"事實就係唔駛付出都大把人爭住埋單"},{"pid":"ab254de5051310b9219a9ffaa0a4c8dc1fc5f146","tid":1025482,"uid":224885,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ce6606bb13edd4db58f15aa5ec77f4fddb1e3df","tid":1025482,"uid":27064,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"事實就係唔駛付出都大把人爭住埋單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"搞到自己似隻臭雞咁 又唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5fa8339a20d0ffd37b1b4a7fba2c221ad3e362","tid":1025482,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5842975ede3e847efb522cc8a7234f9e67ec11dc","tid":1025482,"uid":158411,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/203442_b5a5301b91a9c6d5ce0dfe9ee7a950f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2